title: Get Ready For The Long-Haul With The Gemini Travel Pack
description:
It's clean on the outside and organized on the inside. A 270 degree zipper gives easy access to multiple pockets and sleeves on the move; open the zipper all the way for super efficient packing and unpacking. The Gemini pack allows you to travel in style with all your essentials in reach.
Loaded with features including:
- TSA compliant padded laptop sleeve (fits most 15" laptops)
- Fleece lined padded iPad sleeve
- 270 degree zipper opening on main compartment
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Back panel security pocket
- Quick access pocket
- Interior water bottle pocket
- Headphone pocket
- Multiple accessory pockets
